cast.overview: A live broadcast of a late-night talk show in 1977 goes horribly wrong, unleashing evil into the nation's living rooms.
cast.title: Late Night with the Devil

details.biography: Ingrid Torelli, Actress. Ingrid is an Australian actress known for her work on Late Night with the Devil, Force of Nature, Bloom Season 2 (2020), The End (2020), Five Bedrooms (2019-2020), The Mirror (2020), Holy Spirit (2019), They Can't Hear You (2018), One Last Leaf (2018) and Red and Blue (2017). Ingrid played Matilda in the Melbourne season of Matilda the Musical in 2016 before turning her focus to film and television.
details.name: Ingrid Torelli
